<L>__{interior bartholomew's later}
<A>__{a general store in the township of holmesville. solomon stands at the counter as bartholomew fills mistress epps's order. among the items set before solomon is a}
<B>__{quantity of foolscap.}
<A>__{the items are collected for solomon and placed in a sack. solomon giving little thought to them other than getting them back to the mistress. as he turns, he glimpses the regalia of slave restraints, of all different guises; chains, muzzles for sale.}
